data.description: Welcome to this spacious 2-story townhome with a full finished basement! 1st floor master bedroom & master bath with double sinks, fireplace in living room, beautiful oak staircase, hardwood flooring on 1st and 2nd floors, plus the kitchen features maple cabinets, quartz countertops, and stainless steel appliances. 2nd level has 2 additional bedrooms, a newly remodeled full bath with double sinks, and a loft area overlooking the living room. Half bath also newly remodeled. Full finished basement features TWO bonus rooms and an additional full bath. Roof was replaced by association 3 years ago, the water heater is only 2 years old and water softener was upgraded to a Culligan 5 years ago. Make your appointment today!
